## 12. Explain deployment strategies used in project

### Blue-Green Deployment

* Two identical environments
* Switch traffic after validation
* Easy rollback

### Rolling Deployment

* Deploy gradually to instances
* No downtime

### Canary Deployment

* Release to small users first
* Monitor before full rollout

### Recreate Deployment

* Stop old version then deploy new version
* Used for non-critical apps

